# Termite mushroom is usually 188 CNY for 1 jin (0.5 kg), but we can replace it with oyster mushroom, and the cost comes down to 10 CNY. Once cooked, oyster mushroom is fragrant, crispy, crunchy, and tastes as good as termite mushroom. You can also add "Xiaomila" chili pepper if you love the spicy food. Da Ye had two pieces of "Xiaomila", and was sweating non-stop😥.
