# 原料：平菇、馒头、芝麻、葱、姜、酱油、老抽、白糖、小米辣、食盐、淀粉
# Ingredients: Oyster mushroom, Mantou, sesame seeds, green onions, ginger, soy sauce, dark soy sauce, sugar, Xiaomila chili pepper, salt and starch
# 步骤：
# Steps:
# 1.平菇洗净撕成丝，油温五成热下锅，大火炸干成金黄捞出
# 1. Pull the oyster mushroom into shreds and drop it in oil that is about 150C. Fry on high heat and take it out once it becomes dry and golden brown.
# 2.热锅倒入油，加入葱、姜，之后加入酱油、老抽、白糖，及炸好的平菇丝、芝麻，翻炒均匀，加入小米辣出锅。
# 2. Heat up the wok and pour oil in. Add green onion, ginger, followed by soy sauce, dark soy sauce, sugar and fried oyster mushroom and sesame seeds. Mix all the ingredients well then add Xiaomila chili peppers.
# 3.凉馒头切片，清水中加入食盐、淀粉，馒头片过淀粉水，入油锅炸酥脆，出锅，开饭！
# 3. Slice cold Mantou. Add salt, starch and mix. Dip Mantou slices in the starchy water, then drop it in the hot oil. Fry until crispy and golden brown. Time to eat!

